{"tid":311210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拗柴咁耐都未康復 好無助 好頹廢！點算好","createTime":"2017-07-06T12:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T11:30:11.000Z","uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f77bf489a7adcfde73b00be23a1c8ea275c811","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"有無巴打們試過拗柴超過半年都未好得返？<br />\n事關我之前打波扭到腳腕，之後照左x光話啲骨無事，咁我就以為放心好快應該好返啦，但到依家已經接近半年，我隻腳仲係會有小小腫，特別係有時行得多，我到依家已經睇過幾十次跌打，但都未好返曬，加上我返學，真係睇到破產，唉有無啲跌打師傅好勁又信得過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家咁到我行路行到無扭到個隻腳都好似勞損埋（腳眼膝頭成日唔舒服）唉，呢幾個月真係好sad好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有類似情況？睇跌打？有無介紹<br />\n我洗唔洗去做磁力共振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216d1a7572519febc8d1277c2b5be28bee9c389b","tid":311210,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪聽啲跌打佬講唔好郁佢跟就真成日坐<br />\n你要間唔中郁下佢做下運動先快好 （唔係指打波個啲）<br />\n例如間中轉下隻腳 郁下佢 後尾好少少就可以游水 <br />\n拗過幾次柴之後領悟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17115fbe2a3315fb292c5682d97fbca301e283b","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪聽啲跌打佬講唔好郁佢跟就真成日坐<br />\n你要間唔中郁下佢做下運動先快好 （唔係指打波個啲）<br />\n例如間中轉下隻腳 郁下佢 後尾好少少就可以游水 <br />\n拗過幾次柴之後領悟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲就話唔好郁咁多同行少啲，我一開頭兩個月成日坐，搞到盆骨好酸<br />\n游水真係得？因為我返工個度可以游水，我會嘗試下，唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隻腳腕仲有啲酸緊，郁大力啲都好似有啲酸痛"},{"pid":"55a7f920ac7bdcaf6f4a9e3e2e60baa7dd5e4613","tid":311210,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪聽啲跌打佬講唔好郁佢跟就真成日坐<br />\n你要間唔中郁下佢做下運動先快好 （唔係指打波個啲）<br />\n例如間中轉下隻腳 郁下佢 後尾好少少就可以游水 <br />\n拗過幾次柴之後領悟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲就話唔好郁咁多同行少啲，我一開頭兩個月成日坐，搞到盆骨好酸<br />\n游水真係得？因為我返工個度可以游水，我會嘗試下，唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隻腳腕仲有啲酸緊，郁大力啲都好似有啲酸痛</blockquote><br />\n唔好搏命游 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n志在被個關節活動下廢事硬晒<br />\n個排做返啲運動真係覺得隻腳舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312cc03f41a69a8c14e79dcf9f239d71bb339ece","tid":311210,"uid":11283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:57:41.000Z","msg":"大角咀黃蓉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾次大拗都5次左右搞惦<br />\n有時會見到陳浩南兩公婆去睇"},{"pid":"6331236522344e76f97ce21567e14ca055884401","tid":311210,"uid":125317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"成年先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪岩岩拗果陣冇好好抖同沖左熱水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇跌打都叫我游下水，但唔識游"},{"pid":"a8ecd9c32fb409e3a06086fb937163a05e1b5889","tid":311210,"uid":86355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"照X光好似睇唔到韌帶, 磁力共振先睇到， 但係照到斷左，又會唔會做手術先？"},{"pid":"8725451515e3d37cd7d6d2e923d39eeb4ca91a77","tid":311210,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"訓覺搵啲野&quot;浪&quot;高隻腳<br />\n間唔中轉下佢 好快好返"},{"pid":"ba9838e928af840625dae519f547e945d06ead18","tid":311210,"uid":29229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴打們試過拗柴超過半年都未好得返？<br />\n事關我之前打波扭到腳腕，之後照左x光話啲骨無事，咁我就以為放心好快應該好返啦，但到依家已經接近半年，我隻腳仲係會有小小腫，特別係有時行得多，我到依家已經睇過幾十次跌打，但都未好返曬，加上我返學，真係睇到破產，唉有無啲跌打師傅好勁又信得過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家咁到我行路行到無扭到個隻腳都好似勞損埋（腳眼膝頭成日唔舒服）唉，呢幾個月真係好sad好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有類似情況？睇跌打？有無介紹<br />\n我洗唔洗去做磁力共振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去睇物理治療啦巴打 多數有兩個原因<br />\n1. 條韌帶未好番<br />\n2. 關節出左事緊曬 腳骨有啲移位"},{"pid":"a92f14997e831fcbdd264c39f8da1b9e3d0a05c6","tid":311210,"uid":107269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"唔好撚信跌打啦<br />\n我年青時都試過<br />\n又係睇跌打唔掂<br />\n<br />\n一睇物理治癒即搞掂<br />\n但拖得太耐先睇<br />\n到而家始終都唔係斷哂尾<br />\n返風落雨總會有少少痛"},{"pid":"5725e3d1c19abc718d1a1ca83babf239ebbfa460","tid":311210,"uid":116203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"而家仲有人信跌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多垃圾亂咁黎醫搞到仲衰，完全係冇根據亂鳩咁黎，呃錢事小，愈整就愈傷事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d去睇物理治療啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3171ac8592536153e792029830b9b566aefdd93","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好撚信跌打啦<br />\n我年青時都試過<br />\n又係睇跌打唔掂<br />\n<br />\n一睇物理治癒即搞掂<br />\n但拖得太耐先睇<br />\n到而家始終都唔係斷哂尾<br />\n返風落雨總會有少少痛</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n巴打邊間物理治療好呀<br />\n同埋幾錢架 個程序係點架？<br />\n因為我未試過睇物理治療呀，唔該巴打"},{"pid":"d0b9a3c605128ea80f2228c4ddcf3977d4a4748e","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家仲有人信跌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多垃圾亂咁黎醫搞到仲衰，完全係冇根據亂鳩咁黎，呃錢事小，愈整就愈傷事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d去睇物理治療啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 我依家都對跌打好失望。睇左咁多次都係咁，都唔知係咪hea9我 良心舖頭太少！<br />\n巴打邊間物理治療好呀 我未睇過呀有無推介？<br />\n仲有睇物理治療係有咩程序做？好似睇醫生咁？<br />\n物理治療係做啲咩黎架<br />\n唔該巴打解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40ab00761d8863c4578bdde7c6e0908c2c08ef4","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓覺搵啲野&quot;浪&quot;高隻腳<br />\n間唔中轉下佢 好快好返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前有 但浪得耐會痺"},{"pid":"f06c25fcbb341601f9470b601e5ae3f5d4f98a10","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大角咀黃蓉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾次大拗都5次左右搞惦<br />\n有時會見到陳浩南兩公婆去睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解上網搵唔到間野？ 係邊架"},{"pid":"086219e62a09bfdd97f33afc5ab06f8b1ca1706e","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照X光好似睇唔到韌帶, 磁力共振先睇到， 但係照到斷左，又會唔會做手術先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無想過要開刀咁嚴重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba3481ed19a1d4f92810768a97c744a5b314429","tid":311210,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成年先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪岩岩拗果陣冇好好抖同沖左熱水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇跌打都叫我游下水，但唔識游</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哇成年 你點捱過呢段日子架？<br />\n依家完全好返？你最後睇咩而好返？<br />\n唔該巴打"},{"pid":"cdb9f32aa7beb5b140153e4ca0666ab569efc53e","tid":311210,"uid":116203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家仲有人信跌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多垃圾亂咁黎醫搞到仲衰，完全係冇根據亂鳩咁黎，呃錢事小，愈整就愈傷事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d去睇物理治療啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 我依家都對跌打好失望。睇左咁多次都係咁，都唔知係咪hea9我 良心舖頭太少！<br />\n巴打邊間物理治療好呀 我未睇過呀有無推介？<br />\n仲有睇物理治療係有咩程序做？好似睇醫生咁？<br />\n物理治療係做啲咩黎架<br />\n唔該巴打解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我未睇過，我自己打波整親會去醫院睇針灸，之後再睇youtube 操番受傷果part d肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等其他巴打答你物理治鳩d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff0e308c4e5f45c788d006622f4a19f906000e7","tid":311210,"uid":29229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家仲有人信跌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多垃圾亂咁黎醫搞到仲衰，完全係冇根據亂鳩咁黎，呃錢事小，愈整就愈傷事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d去睇物理治療啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 係呀 我依家都對跌打好失望。睇左咁多次都係咁，都唔知係咪hea9我 良心舖頭太少！<br />\n巴打邊間物理治療好呀 我未睇過呀有無推介？<br />\n仲有睇物理治療係有咩程序做？好似睇醫生咁？<br />\n物理治療係做啲咩黎架<br />\n唔該巴打解答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇醫生拎張referral<br />\n去公立排/去private clinic"},{"pid":"477d011e7def418e63faa1190412f374fd27ac96","tid":311210,"uid":84625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成年先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪岩岩拗果陣冇好好抖同沖左熱水涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇跌打都叫我游下水，但唔識游</blockquote><br />\n浸下水 踢下水其實都ok"},{"pid"